node.text: Ooooh lookie! It’s a cutie with a mouth full of green yums!!! Must have been a delicious snack worth the mess 🤣

@optimus.pet Lol I bet mama didn’t think I was cute when I always ended up with this green beard and she has to use the wet towel to clean me a few times after every feeding session 😂😂😂 It was really funny though 🤣

Help! 🆘 I turned into a green-bearded monster! 🤣 Mummy doesn’t know whether to laugh or cry, and I’m not sure if the problem lies with her not knowing how to feed me or me not knowing how to ingest powder properly 🤭 I love my @optimus.pet supplements, we welcome any suggestions to better manage the feeding 🐶🤦🏻‍♀️😅
